article_id:684,category_name:News,title_name:Summon Showcase: Dragon Special Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>The Summon Showcase: Dragon Special kicked off <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566885600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>During this showcase, the appearance rates for featured 4★ and 5★ dragons will be boosted.</div><div><br></div><div>Regarding Appearance Rate Changes in the Summon Showcase: Dragon Special<br>Starting with this summon showcase, the appearance rates for 5★ featured dragons, 5★ featured adventurers, 5★ dragons, 4★ featured dragons, and 4★ featured adventurers in the Summon Showcase: Dragon Special will be changed as detailed below.<br>Note: Adventurers have been removed from the featured group.</div><div><br></div><div>・5★ featured dragons</div><div>Before: 1.50%</div><div>After: 2.40%</div><div><br></div><div>・5★ featured adventurers</div><div>Before: 0.50%</div><div>After: 0%</div><div><br></div><div>・5★ dragons</div><div>Before: 1.25%</div><div>After: 0.85%</div><div><br></div><div>・4★ featured dragons</div><div>Before: 5.25%</div><div>After: 7.00%</div><div><br></div><div>・4★ featured adventurers</div><div>Before: 1.75%</div><div>After: 0%</div><div><br></div><div>Dragon Special Appearance Rates:</div><div>5★ featured - Total: 2.40% (Adventurers: 0%, Dragons: 2.4%)</div><div>5★ normal - Total: 1.6% (Adventurers: 0.75%, Dragons: 0.85%)</div><div>4★ featured - Total: 7.00% (Adventurers: 0%, Dragons: 7%)</div><div>4★ normal - Total: 9.00% (Adventurers: 5.05%, Dragons: 3.95%)</div><div>3★ normal - Total: 80.00% (Adventurers: 48.00%, Dragons: 32.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>This showcase will be available from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566885600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567231140"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured Dragons:</div><div><div class="summonPickUp">
